LCNG is a LCARS-NG theme for Drupal 6 by G. Nguyen. It is originally based on the sub-theme GENESIS. This theme was inspired by the LCARS-GUI from Star Trek: The Next Generation (TNG)
LCARS-NG is an acronym for "LIBRARY COMPUTER ACCESS/RETRIEVAL SYSTEM â€“ NEXT GENERATION"

FEATURES
- CSS rounded-corners techniques for optimal curves (javascript fallback for the internet explorer with CURVYCORNERS)
- dynamically fullwindow bars and L-bows with auto height if content fits window height
- different layouts for optimal content display
- context layouts
- support drupal menusystem in sidebar-menus
- user profile page

INSTALL
- Just download the files and put it in your Drupal theme folder in "/sites/all/themes" and enjoy :)

PROJECT INFO
Project status: Beta
Drupal version: 6.x
